headline: Twilio Set to Join S&P MidCap 400
summary: Twilio Inc. (NYSE: TWLO) will replace Amedisys Inc. (NASD: AMED) in the S&P MidCap 400 effective prior to the opening of trading on Tuesday, August 19. S&P 500 and S&P 100 constituent UnitedHealth Group Inc. (NYSE: UNH) acquired Amedisys in a deal completed today.
